About Event

​🚀 Kicking off 2026: The Pre-Healthcare Week Hike

​We are starting next year with a bang! Before the chaos of the J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference begins, come clear your head and connect with the community.

​We’re teaming up with the kind folks at MBC BioLabs to host this special kickoff event.

​The Trail: We’ll be doing the Presidio Promenade, Coastal Trail, and Park Loop. Expect iconic Golden Gate views and fresh ocean air.
